<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Embeds Programados</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-[#313338] text-gray-100 min-h-screen">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-screen">
        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <%- include('./sections/sidebarSection.ejs') %>

        <!-- Section Content -->
        <div class="w-full flex flex-col lg:grid grid-cols-11">
            <!-- Main Content -->
            <div class="col-span-7 flex-1 p-6">
                <div class="grow space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <div class="mb-4 flex gap-2">
                            <p class="text-xl font-semibold dark:text-gray-100 my-auto">
                                Embeds 
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
                                <a href="/home" class="rounded font-medium text-sm py-0.5 px-1 text-white transition disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed flex bg-[#6d6f78] hover:bg-[#4e5058] dark:bg-[#4e5058] hover:dark:bg-[#6d6f78]">
                                    Crear Nuevo
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="-mt-2 mb-2">
                            Haz click en el expandible para ver los embeds que pertenecen a un grupo. También puedes ver una previsualización del embed programado haciendo click en el mismo.
                        </p>

                        <!-- Embeds List -->
                        <ul class="text-center space-y-1.5 mt-3" id="embedsList">
                            <li class="mt-24">Cargando...</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Preview Section -->
            <%- include('./sections/previewSection.ejs') %>
        </div> 
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/marked/marked.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://momentjs.com/downloads/moment.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/embedsList.js" type="module"></script>
    <script src="/js/navbar.js"></script>
</body>
</html>